      {
        "id": "C3id_NW768-YQXNd",
        "title": "Text 4",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<h2>Making Changes</h2><p>Now that you got the program to calculate 10 - 4.5, can you get it to calculate the opposite: 4.5 - 10?</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "N81bnLxqCG4TSmjA",
        "title": "Finding Different Ways",
        "content": {
          "type": "Question",
          "version": 1,
          "locked": false,
          "questionId": "2hjmYU",
          "tiles": [
            {
              "title": "Question Prompt",
              "fixedPosition": true,
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p>Once you figured out a way to calculate 4.5 - 10, find a group who figured out a different way.</p><p>Drag this question tile over and explain what your group figured out and what their group figured out.</p>"
                ]
              }
